data.description: Welcome to a homeowner's dream in the exclusive gated community of Lehi Crossing! This residence offers a well-thought-out split floor plan, boasting 4 beds, 2 full baths, & a spacious great room. As you step into the heart of the home, you'll be captivated by the open kitchen that overlooks the great room. The kitchen is a chef's paradise, featuring an oversized island, sleek granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, & a convenient walk-in pantry adds to the appeal. You'll love the easy to maintain landscaping and no behind neighbors. Lehi Crossing is not just a place to call home; it's a community that offers a quality lifestyle. Stroll along the walking paths, well-equipped playground, & relish the peace of mind provided by the gated entry. Your dream home awaits-seize it TODAY!
